Eugenie Besserer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eugenie_Besserer 0 Eugenie Besserer (December 25, 1868 – May 28, 1934) was an American actress who starred in silent films and features of the early sound motion-picture era, beginning in 1910.
